quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  3,81,Jab Allah Taalaa ney nabiyon say ehad liya kay jo kuch mein tumhen kitab-o-hikmat doon phir tumharay pass woh rasool aaye jo tumharay pass ki cheez ko sach bataye to tumharay liye uss per eman lana aur uss ki madad kerna zaroori hai. Farmaya kay tum iss kay iqrari ho aur iss per mera zimma ley rahey ho? Sab ney kaha humen iqrar hai farmaya to abb gawah raho aur khud mein bhi tumharay sath gawahon mein hun
  3,82,Pus iss kay baad jo palat jayen woh yaqeenan pooray na farman hain
  3,83,Kiya woh Allah Taalaa kay deen kay siwa aur deen ki talash mein hain? Halankay tamam aasmanon walay aur sab zamin walay Allah Taalaa hi kay farmanbardar hain khushi say hon ya na khushi say sab ussi ki taraf lotaye jayen gay
  3,84,Aap keh dijiye kay hum Allah Taalaa per aur jo kuch hum per utara gaya hai aur jo kuch ibrahim (alh-e-salam) aur ismail (alh-e-salam) aur yaqoob (alh-e-salam) aur unn ki aulad per utara gaya aur jo kuch musa (alh-e-salam) aur essa (alh-e-salam) aur doosray anbiya Allah Taalaa ki taraf say diya gaye unn sab per eman laye hum inn mein say kissi kay darmiyan farq nahi kertay aur hum Allah Taalaa kay farmanbardar hain
  3,85,Jo shaks islam kay siwa aur deen talash keray uss ka deen qabool na kiya jayega aur woh aakhirat mein nuksan paney walon mein hoga
  3,86,Allah Taalaa unn logon ko kaisay hidayat dey ga jo apney eman laney aur rasool ko haqqaniyat ki gawahi denay aur apney pass roshan daleel aajaney kay baad kafir hojayen Allah Taalaa aisay bey insaf logon ko raah-e-raast per nahi laata
  3,87,Inn ki to yehi saza hai kay inn per Allah Taalaa ki aur farishton ki aur tamam logon ki laanat ho
  3,88,Jiss mein yeh hamesha paray rahen gay na to inn say azab halka kiya jayega na enhen mohlat di jaye gi
  3,89,Magar jo log iss kay baad tauba aur islaah ker len to be-shak Allah Taalaa bakshney wala meharban hai
  3,90,Be-shak jo log apney eman laney kay baad kufur keren phir kufur mein barh jayen unn ki tauba hergiz hergiz qabool na ki jaye gi yehi gumrah log hain
  3,91,Haan jo log kufur keren aur martay dum tak kafir rahen unn mein agar koi zamin bhar sona go fidiye mein hi ho to bhi hergiz qabool na kiya jayega yehi log hain jin kay liye takleef denay wala azab hai aur jin ka koi madadgar nahi